author: RTÉ News
title: Exodus from Wuhan as China lifts lockdown
description: The Chinese city where the coronavirus epidemic first broke out, Wuhan, has ended a two-month lockdown, but a northern town has imposed restrictions amid concerns of a second wave of infections in mainland China.
content:
The Chinese city where the coronavirus epidemic first broke out, Wuhan, has ended a two-month lockdown, but a northern town started restricting the movement of its residents amid concerns of a second wave of infections in mainland China.
